---
title: Southwest Tilapia with Charred Corn Salad and Buttery Lime Rice
description: Flaky tilapia takes a trip to the Southwest, thanks to a coating of warm spices like cumin, chili powder, and garlic. After crisping up in the pan, it’s served alongside buttery lime rice and a charred corn salad that’s chock full of fresh veggies and cilantro. For a finishing touch, everything is drizzled with cooling lime crema. This dish is our favorite way to feel summer vibes year round.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w31-r13-southwest-tilapia-6acf9437.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w31-r13-southwest-tilapia-5d07cf27cb6dea00126134fe-a19152a4.pdf
servings: 2
